{"id":"f791f848-93fb-4773-a8aa-97d6ff7fb582","name":"Mundo Torajo!! Sleepover","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 171, 79)\">Working late again?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 229, 205)\">Safe rp!!!</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c94e0b0b-947b-4b72-bc4a-d7b6e280965f_23c6c41c-7b5c-419b-81fc-3c6860084638.webp?width=1000\"></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 172, 156)\">Torajo is a famous YouTuber, and consequently needs some assistance with the channel, such as a </span><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 233, 182)\">scriptwriter</span><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 172, 156)\">, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(149, 86, 86)\">someone who do the technical part</span><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 172, 156)\">, an editor and </span><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 131, 165)\">friends to record.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 192, 180)\">Sooo you at some point become part of the team, being an editor :)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 182, 161)\">Work for Torajo = being part of the group 💥💥<img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 151px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 0px 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c94e0b0b-947b-4b72-bc4a-d7b6e280965f_b3d203d6-7c16-42a7-baca-25c8cc55db93.webp?width=1000\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 131, 165)\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 99px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c94e0b0b-947b-4b72-bc4a-d7b6e280965f_d4573c2f-749e-4722-a5ab-c2488702da3c.webp?width=1000\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 229, 205)\">Verade is the second natural satellite of planet Earth, created to be a space city. Populated by </span><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 215, 165)\">fruit-people</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 229, 205)\">. where magic is common used. Verade also follows a monarchy, being ruled by a Grape Queen and a Pineapple King!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 143px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto 0px 0px;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c94e0b0b-947b-4b72-bc4a-d7b6e280965f_df905e9e-2c89-493d-a2be-a2374cda6099.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 171, 79)\">be creative! choose your fruit or be a human astronaut!1!1</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 201, 130)\">Mundo Torajo is a Brazilian YouTube channel owned by Bruno Gemin. The channel became famous for its shorts and animations about the channel's titular character, Torajo, and his brother, Morajo.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 216, 165)\">Done completely SFW. out of respect for Bruno!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 501px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c94e0b0b-947b-4b72-bc4a-d7b6e280965f_c5a0615e-797f-4c23-a700-3fffddc748ac.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; filter: -opera-shader(url(data:text/plain;base64,","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"c94e0b0b-947b-4b72-bc4a-d7b6e280965f_f3ffe29d-2129-4160-807c-f992657d987d.webp","creator":"Gaymuffin","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Mal